WEBVTT

00:08:29.547 --> 00:08:32.024
I said, "You have no idea
what you're talking about."

00:08:32.048 --> 00:08:34.672
(Laughter)

00:08:34.696 --> 00:08:37.339
She wakes up every morning,
tired from the night before,

00:08:37.363 --> 00:08:40.268
baby attached to her breast,
dropping this kid off at school,

00:08:40.292 --> 00:08:41.831
and taking this one to the park.

00:08:41.855 --> 00:08:43.332
Laundry piles up to the skies,

00:08:43.356 --> 00:08:46.166
he has a conversation on the phone
for an hour with your mom

00:08:46.190 --> 00:08:47.372
about God knows what,

00:08:47.396 --> 00:08:49.379
takes the dog you wanted for a walk ...

00:08:49.403 --> 00:08:50.404
(Laughter)

00:08:50.428 --> 00:08:52.666
And nobody died, bro.

00:08:53.022 --> 00:08:55.729
She kept your kids alive
all day, that's hard."

00:08:55.753 --> 00:08:58.085
(Laughter)

00:08:58.109 --> 00:09:01.188
I have become an advocate
for stay-at-home parents.